data.description: Investors and first time home buyers take note! This 2 bedroom 1 bath bungalow is ready for a new owner. This home is centrally located in North Fort Myers close to shopping, dining and the historic downtown district. It sits on a nice fenced lot with a beautiful oak tree in the front yard. This home offers a maintenance free metal roof as well! The kitchen has been remodeled and the bathroom has a claw foot tub! This would make a great first home or if you are an investor and wanting to add to your portfolio. There are not many homes listed at this price. Call today for your personal showing.
